{"tid":2091263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「台港辦公室」首日營運收 180 項諮詢　包括尋求政治庇護","createTime":"2020-07-02T15:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T15:25:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38f253fdbe4379fa0510222663fa3453d04cb618","tid":2091263,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"《港區國安法》正式實施，在台灣，陸委會副主委兼發言人邱垂正今日 ( 2 日) 出席例行記者會時，表示不會主動撤走駐港辦事處，但會提醒台灣民眾前往香港的風險。另外，「台港服務交流辦公室」昨日 ( 1 日) 正式營運，邱指已收到 180 個諮詢，當中包括尋求政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/陸委會提醒台民眾赴港風險-台港辦公室-首日營運收-180-項諮詢-包括尋求政治庇護/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E5%8F%B0%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E8%B5%B4%E6%B8%AF%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E5%8F%B0%E6%B8%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B%E6%94%B6-180-%E9%A0%85%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=a534b4da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E5%8F%B0%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E8%B5%B4%E6%B8%AF%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E5%8F%B0%E6%B8%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B%E6%94%B6-180-%E9%A0%85%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7%2F&h=1ee9fbe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/陸委會提醒台民眾赴港風險-台港辦公室-首日營運收-180-項諮詢-包括尋求政治庇護/</a>"}]}